OL,3,CIndoor ski centre fined #100k after
OL,4,Cboy, 12, died in slope crash
OL,6,FHe was at a friend's birthday
OL,7,Ftobogganing (sledding) party and was
OL,8,Ftravelling down the slope on a plastic
OL,9,Fsled.
OL,11,FHe crashed with the staff member, who
OL,12,Ffell backwards onto him. Louis
OL,13,Fsuffered skull fractures and died at
OL,14,Fthe scene.
OL,16,FThe staff member was conducting a
OL,17,Fsafety inspection of the slope, the
OL,18,Fcourt heard. He was checking that the
OL,19,Fsnow is in a good condition and enough
OL,20,Fmarshals are deplayed.
