OL,3,CIndoor ski centre fined #100k after
OL,4,Cboy, 12, died in slope crash
OL,6,FSnowDome said it ideally takes place
OL,7,Fbefore the session, but occassionally
OL,8,Fthat was not the case. There was no
OL,9,Fset route for the slope walk and no
OL,10,Ftraining for those who conduct them.
OL,12,FThe staff member was wearing a fully
OL,13,Fblack outfit, not a Hi-Vis top, it was
OL,14,Fnoted.
OL,16,FToboganning is no longer on offer at
OL,17,Fthe SnowDome. Helmets are now worn on
OL,18,Fevery activity including ice skating,
OL,19,Fthe centre said.
