OL,3,CIndoor ski centre fined #100k after
OL,4,Cboy, 12, died in slope crash
OL,6,FThe court also saw CCTV footage of a
OL,7,Fsome collisions and near misses
OL,8,Fbetween staff and customers in the two
OL,9,Fweeks before Louis died.
OL,11,FSince his death, Louis's parents Chris
OL,12,Fand Natalie Watkiss have campaigned to
OL,13,Fmake helmets mandatory for children at
OL,14,Findoor ski slopes.
OL,16,FMr Mitchell wrote a letter to then-
OL,17,FCulture Secretary Nadine Dorries
OL,18,Fcalling for the change, and said "the
OL,19,Fcoroner's verdict confirms that there
OL,20,Fis little doubt that a helmet would
OL,21,Fhave saved his life."
